quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,94,"“Ambuje ŵangu! Basi ngasimundenda kuŵa muŵandu ŵalupuso.”"
  23,95,"Sano Uwwe chisimu chene pa yakunnosya (ilagasyo) yaakuŵa nkupedwa chilanga ŵanganyao tuŵele ŵakombola kusyene."
  23,96,"Tyosyani yakusakala (yanteendeele) pa (kwateendela) ayila yaili yambone. Uwwe tukumanyilila chenene yaakusimbayo."
  25,40,"Soni chisimu ŵanganyao (achimakafili ŵa pa Maaka m’maulendo gao gakuja ku Shami), akasaupitaga musi (wa Sodomu) awula wana kumputilaga ula jakusakala (jamaganga), ana ngaakasaŵaga ali nkuuona? Nambo kuti akuŵaga akakwembecheya yakwimuka m’malembe, (niligongo lyakwe ngaakukulupililaga)."
  25,41,"Soni ndema jaakum’bona mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) ngaakuntenda inepe ikaŵeje chipongwe (pakuŵecheta kuti): “Ana aju ni jwantumisye Allah kuŵa ntenga?”"
  25,42,"“Jwaasigele panandi kuti atusochelesye kuleka milungu jetu, ingaŵaga kuti twapililile pa jalakwejo.” Sano ŵanganyao tachiika kumanyilila ndema jatachiiona ilagasyo kuti nduni jwakusokonechela nnope kwitala (lyagoloka)."
  26,13,"“Ni chikaŵanikwe chidali changu (ligongo lyakunganila), nambo soni lulimi lwangu ngalukuchachukaga chenene, basi tumisyani (soni utengau) kwa Haruna (kuti akangamusyeje).”"
  26,14,"“Soni ŵanganyao akwete magambo ganaleŵele, ni ngogopa kuti takambulaje.”"
  26,15,"Allah) jwatite: “Ngwamba! Basi jaulani ŵanaŵaŵilimmwe ni isimosimo Yetu. Chisimu Uwwe chitukaŵe namwe imo (pakunkamuchisya) aku tuchipikanilaga (yatakaŵecheteje).”"